---
config:
  theme: dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client / SDK
    participant Frontend as Dynamo Frontend + KV Router<br/>(Gateway / API / Routing / KV Index State)
    participant Sidecar as Dynamo Sidecar
    participant Engine as Native Engine Server<br/>(vLLM / TRT-LLM / SGLang)

    Client->>Frontend: Send request<br/>(prompt, params, stream=true)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Authenticate / authorize
    Frontend->>Frontend: Normalize to Dynamo request schema
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select worker using KV router

    Frontend->>Sidecar: Forward Dynamo request

    Sidecar->>Sidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine request schema
    Sidecar->>Engine: Invoke engine over OpenEngine API

    Engine->>Engine: Normalize to engine-native request schema
    Engine->>Engine: Begin execution<br/>(prefill and/or decode)

    Engine-->>Sidecar: Stream partial response over OpenEngine API<br/>(tokens, usage, intermediate status)
    Sidecar->>Sidecar: Normalize to Dynamo response schema
    Sidecar-->>Frontend: Stream partial Dynamo response
    Frontend-->>Client: Stream partial response

    Client->>Frontend: Cancel request<br/>(client disconnect / explicit cancel)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Mark request as cancelled
    Frontend->>Sidecar: Send Dynamo cancellation<br/>(request id)

    Sidecar->>Sidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine cancellation schema
    Sidecar->>Engine: Cancel request over OpenEngine API

    Engine->>Engine: Normalize to engine-native cancellation
    Engine->>Engine: Stop scheduling / generation<br/>release request resources

    Engine-->>Sidecar: Acknowledge cancellation over OpenEngine API
    Sidecar->>Sidecar: Normalize to Dynamo cancellation result
    Sidecar-->>Frontend: Acknowledge Dynamo cancellation

    Frontend->>Frontend: Finalize cancelled request state
    Frontend-->>Client: Stop response stream

    par Event plane
        Engine-->>Sidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(cancel requested / cancel acknowledged / KV cleanup / metrics)
        Sidecar->>Sidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        Sidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(request cancelled / capacity released / KV metadata updated)
    and State update
        Frontend->>Frontend: Update KV router state<br/>(request status, worker capacity, KV index)
    end
